{"tid":763820,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳亦凡新口頭禪「skr」爆紅　陳冠希爆粗留言暗串不了解嘻哈精神","createTime":"2018-08-01T12:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T15:13:57.000Z","uid":165934,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"36b561a186594babca22d15fedff7b41080d713e","tid":763820,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:16:49.000Z","msg":"內地綜藝節目《中國新說唱》已經正式開始，除了G.E.M.最初寫Rap狠狠反擊Haters之後，吳亦凡再次成為了焦點。因為他在節目又有新口頭禪「skr」，後來網民廣泛使用，就連Mc HotDog也被感染到，動不動就skr。<br />\n<br />\n吳亦凡多次在節目上講「skr skr」，引起網民熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n「skr skr」有多個意思，第一個是汽車輪胎打轉的聲音；第二個就是遇到荒謬的人和事，就可以用「skr」代替掩臉；而第三個意思就是沒有意思，不過被吳亦凡用過後，就有很讚的意思。<br />\n<br />\n節目裡不停聽到「skr skr」一詞之後，McHotDog後來也跟機一起「Skr」，他在IG說：「我最近發現用skr造句還蠻好玩的耶！例如：我是根熱狗，我skr熱狗，我不懂skr而止，我只skr愛打電動的宅男。」<br />\n<br />\n可是熱狗的朋友陳冠希可不是這樣想，他甚至爆粗留言，大約意思是：「這個玩意兒真可笑，這些人不懂自己在說甚麼，卻覺得自己很酷？這文化到底怎麼了？」<br />\n<br />\n網民見到陳冠希留言反應兩極，有人認為他沒份擔任《中國新說唱》評判所以生氣，覺得他自以為是；也有人認為他講出事實，歷史會證明他是對的。<br />\n<br />\nSkt <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d91cbb3168233517ac537a86453cc5745f9bce","tid":763820,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36b561a186594babca22d15fedff7b41080d713e","tid":763820,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:16:49.000Z","msg":"內地綜藝節目《中國新說唱》已經正式開始，除了G.E.M.最初寫Rap狠狠反擊Haters之後，吳亦凡再次成為了焦點。因為他在節目又有新口頭禪「skr」，後來網民廣泛使用，就連Mc HotDog也被感染到，動不動就skr。<br />\n<br />\n吳亦凡多次在節目上講「skr skr」，引起網民熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n「skr skr」有多個意思，第一個是汽車輪胎打轉的聲音；第二個就是遇到荒謬的人和事，就可以用「skr」代替掩臉；而第三個意思就是沒有意思，不過被吳亦凡用過後，就有很讚的意思。<br />\n<br />\n節目裡不停聽到「skr skr」一詞之後，McHotDog後來也跟機一起「Skr」，他在IG說：「我最近發現用skr造句還蠻好玩的耶！例如：我是根熱狗，我skr熱狗，我不懂skr而止，我只skr愛打電動的宅男。」<br />\n<br />\n可是熱狗的朋友陳冠希可不是這樣想，他甚至爆粗留言，大約意思是：「這個玩意兒真可笑，這些人不懂自己在說甚麼，卻覺得自己很酷？這文化到底怎麼了？」<br />\n<br />\n網民見到陳冠希留言反應兩極，有人認為他沒份擔任《中國新說唱》評判所以生氣，覺得他自以為是；也有人認為他講出事實，歷史會證明他是對的。<br />\n<br />\nSkt <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:17:38.000Z","msg":"Skr <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7a3f25d0293f6ec9a364322add7b47593f6557","tid":763820,"uid":20528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:18:07.000Z","msg":"Cls"},{"pid":"43268d3473394f536d4f59488b91144b2f89aaee","tid":763820,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:20:28.000Z","msg":"做乜撚"},{"pid":"7ae4cbd630c245d56c098817ad38c119e9307dad","tid":763820,"uid":187991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:23:24.000Z","msg":"Skr 凡"},{"pid":"682638102d7a7edb3f090d789e828ebf67dddc27","tid":763820,"uid":197794,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2